text: Sophie Poser née Krauel (born 2 March 1985) is a former German track and field athlete who competed in mainly long jump events. She married her boyfriend Florian Poser in May 2013, he competes in decathlon and they had a baby together in December the same year. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:People from Jena Category:German female long jumpers Category:German female hurdlers Category:German heptathletes Category:German female sprinters
